Compose BioCompute Object (v1.4.2)

compose_v1.4.2(
  tlf,
  provenance,
  usability,
  extension,
  description,
  execution,
  parametric,
  io,
  error
)

compose(
  tlf,
  provenance,
  usability,
  extension,
  description,
  execution,
  parametric,
  io,
  error
)

Arguments

tlf

Top level fields

provenance

Provenance domain

usability

Usability domain

extension

Extension domain

description

Description domain

execution

Execution domain

parametric

Parametric domain

io

I/O domain

error

Error domain

Value

A list of class bco

Examples

tlf <- compose_tlf(
  compose_provenance(), compose_usability(), compose_extension(),
  compose_description(), compose_execution(), compose_parametric(),
  compose_io(), compose_error()
)
biocompute::compose(
  tlf,
  compose_provenance(), compose_usability(), compose_extension(),
  compose_description(), compose_execution(), compose_parametric(),
  compose_io(), compose_error()
) %>% convert_json()
